---

<div class="standard-page">
  <span class="status-tag done">3D MODELING / DESIGN</span>
  <h2>3D WORK</h2>

  <p>
    TGS（東京ゲームショウ）出展のVRシューティングゲームにて、主役機のモデリングおよび武器セットのデザイン・モデリングを担当しました。
  </p>

  <div class="text-gallery">
    <div class="gallery-item large">
      <div class="gallery-img-wrapper">
        <img
          src="/images/works/3D/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%202026-03-06%2015.58.47.png"
          alt="3D Work 05"
        />
      </div>
      <span class="img-caption">Weapon / Equipment Details</span>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery-row">
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <div class="gallery-img-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/works/3D/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%202026-03-06%2015.59.01.png"
            alt="3D Work 06"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <div class="gallery-img-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/works/3D/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%202026-03-06%2015.58.16.png"
            alt="3D Work 07"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <div class="gallery-img-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/works/3D/%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%202026-03-06%2015.57.21.png"
            alt="3D Work 08"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .status-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: #e3ffe3;
    color: #20d120;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #111;
    font-family: "Inter", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .text-gallery {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .gallery-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .gallery-img-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .gallery-img-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .gallery-img-wrapper:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .large .gallery-img-wrapper {
    max-height: 250px;
  }

  .gallery-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .gallery-row .gallery-img-wrapper {
    height: 100px;
  }

  .img-caption {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #999;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
</style>
